About 780 orphans and vulnerable children have been given Sh11.2 million bursary by AphiaPlus. Busia Deputy Governor Kizito Wangalwa (pictured) said no child should be left at home while others are in school. We should work together to ensure all children get an education, he said. AphiaPlus Western Kenya director Bramwel Siku urged the community to support needy children.